articles.title: HTech launch HONOR 90 5G smartphone in UP, to target major cities first - Business Standard
articles.description: Smart devices maker HTech will target major cities of Uttar Pradesh in the first phase to market its smartphone, HONOR 90 5G, which it launched in the state on Monday.
articles.content: Senior vice-president of HTech C P Khandelwal, who was in Lucknow to mark the launch of the smartphone, told PTI, "The launch has been good, and we have launched it on online and offline channels."Sp… [+432 chars]
